Kitui Senator David Musila&rsquo;s mother Alice Musila (pictured) died at dawn on Sunday morning as the world marked Mothers&rsquo; Day.In a WhatsApp group, Musila posted, &ldquo;I thank God for her life. May He rest her soul in eternal peace. Amen.&rdquo;The senator&rsquo;s son Aaron said she died at the Nairobi Hospital, where she had been admitted four weeks ago.&ldquo;She was around 95-years-old and she was suffering from complications related to old age,&rdquo; he said on the phone.